name: TreeList_indexOfTest
description: Unit tests for the indexOf method of the TreeList class.

test_cases.name: testIndexOfWithEmptyList
test_cases.description: Tests the indexOf method with an empty list, expecting -1.

test_cases.name: testIndexOfWithElementPresent
test_cases.description: Tests the indexOf method with an element present in the list, expecting the correct index.

test_cases.name: testIndexOfWithElementNotPresent
test_cases.description: Tests the indexOf method with an element not present in the list, expecting -1.

test_cases.name: testIndexOfWithNullElement
test_cases.description: Tests the indexOf method with a null element in the list, expecting the correct index.

test_cases.name: testIndexOfWithMultipleNullElements
test_cases.description: Tests the indexOf method with multiple null elements in the list, expecting the correct index.
